OL,4,Cat their home
OL,6,FA man who walked into a police station
OL,7,Fand said "I've killed two people" has
OL,8,Fbeen found guilty of murder.
OL,10,FDerek Martin struck Chloe Bashford
OL,11,Fwith a hammer and stabbed her before
OL,12,Fkilling her husband Joshua Bashford at
OL,13,Ftheir home in Newhaven on 9th June
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,FMartin was previously married to Mrs
OL,17,FBashford's mother and was a close
OL,18,Ffriend of the family when he "lost his
OL,19,Ftemper" following a row with Mrs
OL,20,FBashford, believed to be about money.
