OL,6,FWhile Martin was not still in a
OL,7,Frelationship with Mrs Bashford's
OL,8,Fmother, she referred to him as "step
OL,9,Fdad" in a text to her friend the day
OL,10,Fshe died.
OL,12,FFollowing the brutal act of violence,
OL,13,FMartin picked up the Bashford's four
OL,14,Fchildren from school and took them to
OL,15,FCosta and McDonalds before handing
OL,16,Fhimself in.
