OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering couple
OL,4,Cat their home
OL,6,FMartin had denied murder with his
OL,7,Fdefence claiming his history of mental
OL,8,Fhealth problems, which stemmed from an
OL,9,Fabusive childhood, resulted in him
OL,10,Flosing control on the day of the
OL,11,Fkillings.
OL,13,FAfter retiring to consider their
OL,14,Fverdict Brighton Law Courts on
OL,15,FThursday, jurors on Friday morning
OL,16,F(October 24) decided Martin was guilty
OL,17,Fof murder.
OL,19,FThe 67-year old, wearing a grey
OL,20,Ftracksuit, showed no emotion as the
OL,21,Fverdict was read out.
