OL,3,CMan found guilty of murdering couple
OL,4,Cat their home
OL,6,FPreviously the court heard that Martin
OL,7,Fand Mrs Bashford had spent the morning
OL,8,Ftogether before he hit her on the top
OL,9,Fof her head with a hammer. He then
OL,10,Fwent to the kitchen to retrieve a
OL,11,Flarge knife and repeatedly stabbed her.
OL,13,FHe then ambushed Mr Bashford, who had
OL,14,Fcome home early from work, and chased
OL,15,Fhim into an upstairs bedroom before
OL,16,Fstabbing him.
OL,18,FMartin first admitted being
OL,19,Fresponsible for the killings in a
OL,20,Fpolice interview on June 10 2023.
