OL,6,FProsecuting, Julian Evans KC recounted
OL,7,Fthe interview in court: "He said that
OL,8,Fhe felt he was getting 'used' all of
OL,9,Fthe time. He could not do enough for
OL,10,Fpeople, and he had got into a lot of
OL,11,Fdebt himself as well.
OL,13,F"Then he said that he 'just lost it'
OL,14,Fand he 'just flipped'. He hit Chloe on
OL,15,Fthe head with the hammer. He did not
OL,16,Fknow what had happened.
OL,18,F"He said that Josh came in the door.
OL,19,FHe (Martin) was behind the door. He
OL,20,Fsaid that Josh saw him with the knife
OL,21,Fin his hand and he ran upstairs.
